vector-skin-desc:
Kiha empu 2 za Vekitoli:
* 2011 - Omulingo omuhyaka gwa MonoBuki ogwina enzooka empyaka n'enkiza nyingi y'okukozesa.
* 2022 - Vekitoli eyombeka omu kwekamba kwa WMF [[mw:Desktop Improvements]].
prefs-vector-enable-vector-1-help: Omu myaka mitaito y'okwongeraho, tuliba nitukora oruhu rwa Vekitoli. Vekitoli y'Ekirale erikwikiriza kurora omulingo omukuru gwa Vekitoli (gw'Ogwa ikumi n'ebiri 2019). Kwega muno enkora, genda [[mw:Reading/Web/Desktop_Improvements|orupapura rw'okwekamba]] rwaitu.
vector-opt-out-tooltip: Hingisa ebisemezibwa byawe kugaruka enzooka enkuru y'oruhu (Vekitoli y'ekirale)
vector-language-button-aria-label: Genda amakuru omu rudimi rundi. Garoho omu {{PLURAL:$1|rulimi $1|ndimi $1}}
vector-no-language-button-aria-label: Ganu amakuru garoho omu rulimi runu rwonka. Taho amakuru omu ndimi ezindi
vector-language-redirect-to-top: Ebiyunga by'endimi biri haiguru y'orupapura na ha bukiika bw'omutwe.
vector-limited-width-toggle-on-popup: Ohingisiize entegeka yaawe ha bugazi obutatangwa. Kugaruka obugazi obutangwa, miga linu ipeesa.
vector-limited-width-toggle-off-popup: Waakuhinduliza emalirra y'obugazi n'okumiga linu ipeesa.
vector-prefs-limited-width-help: Soboza omulingo gw'obugazi obutangwa habw'ensoma eyekira.
empty-language-selector-body: Tiharoho birumu by'orupapura omu ndimi zindi.
